OL,3,CRace routes revealed for first UK
OL,4,CEuropean Athletics Championships
OL,6,FThe road race routes have been
OL,7,Funveiled for the first-ever UK-based
OL,8,FEuropean Athletics Championships.
OL,10,FThe competition is coming to
OL,11,FBirmingham on 10-16 August.
OL,13,FMost of the events will be based at
OL,14,Fthe Alexander Stadium, as 1600
OL,15,Fathletes from 48 countries compete.
OL,17,FBut over the weekend, the athletes
OL,18,Fwill be taking to the streets of
OL,19,FBirmingham City Centre to compete in
OL,20,Felite race walks and elite marathon
OL,21,Fevents.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
