OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784659707
OL,3,CRace routes revealed for first UK
OL,4,CEuropean Athletics Championships
OL,6,FThe runners include Birmingham athlete
OL,7,FEllis Cross, who is competing in the
OL,8,Fmen's marathon for the Great Britain
OL,9,Fand Northern Ireland team.
OL,11,FThe 1km race walks will take place on
OL,12,FAugust 15th, starting on Colmore Row
OL,13,Fand finishing at Victoria Square.
OL,15,FSpectators will be able to watch along
OL,16,FWaterloo Street, Temple Row West, and
OL,17,FColmore Row.
OL,19,FAnd the men's and women's marathons
OL,20,Fwill take place on the Championships'
OL,21,Ffinal day - August 16th.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
