CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784659707
OL,3,CRace routes revealed for first UK
OL,4,CEuropean Athletics Championships
OL,6,FThe men's and women's marathons will
OL,7,Fboth start in Victoria Square and
OL,8,Finvolve 8 laps of a city centre
OL,9,Fcircuit.
OL,11,FOrganisers recommend watching the
OL,12,Fmarathon, which begins at 7:30am and
OL,13,F8:10am along Colmore Row and Church
OL,14,FStreet, Holliday Street, Granville
OL,15,FStreet, Sheepcote Street, Sand Pits,
OL,16,FLudgate Hill, Charlotte Street, and
OL,17,FWarstone Lane.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
