PN,34804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784659707
OL,3,CRace routes revealed for first UK
OL,4,CEuropean Athletics Championships
OL,6,FCherry Alexander, Championship
OL,7,FDirector for Birmingham 2026, said:
OL,8,F"In three weeks, Birmingham will host
OL,9,Fthe UK's first-ever European Athletics
OL,10,FChampionships, creating an
OL,11,Funforgettable sporting moment for the
OL,12,Fcity and the nation.
OL,14,F"With the elite race walks and
OL,15,Fmarathon taking place on Birmingham's
OL,16,Fstreets, people can get closer than
OL,17,Fever to the action and watch some of
OL,18,Fthe world's best athletes compete in
OL,19,Ficonic city-centre locations.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784659707
OL,3,CRace routes revealed for first UK
OL,4,CEuropean Athletics Championships
OL,6,F"The enthusiasm and support of local
OL,7,Fcommunities, visitors, and athletics
OL,8,Ffans from across Europe will create an
OL,9,Fincredible atmosphere and help make
OL,10,FBirmingham 2026 a truly memorable
OL,11,FChampionships."
OL,13,FAfter the marathon finishes, there
OL,14,Fwill be a 1K and 5K race for members
OL,15,Fof the public, where runners can earn
OL,16,Ftheir own medal.
OL,18,FThe fun runs will begin on Broad
OL,19,FStreet and finish in Victoria Square.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
