OL,3,CRace routes revealed for first UK
OL,4,CEuropean Athletics Championships
OL,6,FYou can buy tickets for the European
OL,7,FChampionships now to see stars like
OL,8,Fworld-record holder Mondo Duplantis
OL,9,Fand Olympic champion Keely Hodgkinson.
